JobDefinitionSteps.Name: Customer/Product
JobDefinitionSteps.SelectClause:
trim(ciitno) as ProductNumber,
trim(cicsno) as CustomerNumber,
'' as CustomerSequence,
cicsit as CustomerPartNumber,
duunms as UnitOfMeasure
JobDefinitionSteps.FromClause:
iaxrf
join itmst on itmst.imitno = iaxrf.ciitno 
join cusms on cusms.cmcono = iaxrf.cicono and cusms.cmcsno = iaxrf.cicsno
left join cdfum on cdfum.ducono = iaxrf.cicono 
  and cdfum.ducsno = iaxrf.cicsno 
  and cdfum.duitno = iaxrf.ciitno
JobDefinitionSteps.WhereClause:
iaxrf.cicono = 1 and
cusms.cmsusp = '' and
(itmst.imcono = 0 or itmst.imcono = 1) and itmst.imsusp <> 'S' and itmst.impwbu <> 'Y' and
not exists (select 1 from iaxrf X2 where x2.cicono = iaxrf.cicono and x2.cicsno = iaxrf.cicsno and
x2.ciitno = iaxrf.ciitno and x2.cicsit > iaxrf.cicsit)

Name: APlus02: Codes Refresh
Description: A+ Standard A/R Terms & Carriers Refresh

JobDefinitionSteps.Name: Carriers
JobDefinitionSteps.SelectClause:
trim(substring(ccctlk,3)) as ShipVia,
substring(ccdata,1,30) as Description
JobDefinitionSteps.WhereClause:
cccono = 0 and
ccapid = 'OE' and
ccrccd = 'CR' and
ccctlk like 'CC%'

JobDefinitionSteps.Name: Ship Vias
JobDefinitionSteps.SelectClause:
trim(substring(ccctlk,3)) as ShipVia,
substring(ccdata,1,30) as Description
JobDefinitionSteps.WhereClause:
cccono = 0 and
ccapid = 'OE' and
ccrccd = 'CR' and
ccctlk like 'CC%'

JobDefinitionSteps.Name: Terms
JobDefinitionSteps.SelectClause:
substring(ccctlk,6) as TermsCode,
substring(ccdata,1,20) as Description,
current_date as ActivateOn
JobDefinitionSteps.WhereClause:
cccono = 1 and 
ccapid = 'AR' and
ccrccd = 'AT' and
substring(ccctlk,1,5) = '@TRMS'

JobDefinitionSteps.Name: Cross Sells
JobDefinitionSteps.SelectClause:
trim(mrorit) as ProductNumber,
trim(mrrpit) as RelatedProductNumber,
'ProductRelationship' as ListType,
CASE mrrpcd
  WHEN 'A' then 'Accessory'
  WHEN 'C' then 'CrossSell'
END as ListValue
JobDefinitionSteps.FromClause:
imxrf join itmst prod1 on prod1.imitno = imxrf.mrorit
join itmst  prod2 on prod2.imitno = imxrf.mrrpit
JobDefinitionSteps.WhereClause:
(mrrpcd = 'A' or mrrpcd = 'C') and
(prod1.imcono = 0 or prod1.imcono = 1) and prod1.imsusp <> 'S' and prod1.impwbu <> 'Y' and
(prod2.imcono = 0 or prod2.imcono = 1) and prod2.imsusp <> 'S' and prod2.impwbu <> 'Y'

JobDefinitionSteps.Name: Vendors
JobDefinitionSteps.SelectClause:
pvvnno as VendorNumber,
pvvnnm as Name,
pvvad1 as Address1,
pvvad2 as Address2,
pvvcty as City,
pvvnst as State,
pvvzip as PostalCode,
pvctcd as Country,
pvvcnt as ContactName
JobDefinitionSteps.WhereClause: pvvnno in (select distinct Imvnno from itmst)

JobDefinitionSteps.Name: Restriction Groups
JobDefinitionSteps.SelectClause:
trim(substring(ccctlk,2)) as GroupName,
substring(ccdata,1,30) as Description,
CASE WHEN substring(ccdata,31,1) = 'A' THEN 'Show' ELSE 'Hide' END as DisplayType
JobDefinitionSteps.FromClause:
orctl
where cccono = 0 and
ccapid = 'OE' and
ccctlk like '*%'
UNION ALL
SELECT DISTINCT
trim(cacsno) || CASE WHEN cashp# <> '' THEN ':' ELSE '' END || trim(cashp#) as GroupName,
cmcsnm as Description,
CASE WHEN substring(orctl.ccctlk,31,1) = 'A' then 'Show' ELSE 'Hide' END as DisplayType
FROM
oecau join itmst on imitno = caitno
LEFT JOIN orctl on orctl.cccono = 0 and orctl.ccapid = 'OE' and orctl.ccctlk = concat('*',itmst.imrscd)
JOIN cusms on cacsno = cmcsno
JobDefinitionSteps.WhereClause:
carscd = '' and
cmsusp = '' and
cacscc * 1000000 + cacsdt < (year(current_date) * 10000 + month(current_date) * 100 + day(current_date)) and
(year(current_date) * 10000 + month(current_date) * 100 + day(current_date)) < cacecc * 1000000 + cacedt

JobDefinitionSteps.Name: Customer-Specific Products
JobDefinitionSteps.SelectClause:
trim(cacsno) || CASE WHEN cashp# <> '' THEN ':' ELSE '' END || trim(cashp#) as GroupName,
trim(cacsno) as CustomerNumber,
trim(cashp#) as CustomerSequence,
trim(caitno) as ItemNumber
JobDefinitionSteps.FromClause:
oecau join
cusms on cacsno = cmcsno
JobDefinitionSteps.WhereClause:
cacono = 1 and
caitno <> '' and
cmsusp = '' and
cacscc * 1000000 + cacsdt < (year(current_date) * 10000 + month(current_date) * 100 + day(current_date)) and
(year(current_date) * 10000 + month(current_date) * 100 + day(current_date)) < cacecc * 1000000 + cacedt

JobDefinitionSteps.Name: Assign Customers to Restriction Groups
JobDefinitionSteps.SelectClause:
trim(cacsno) as CustomerNumber,
trim(cashp#) as CustomerSequence,
trim(carscd) as RestrictionGroup
JobDefinitionSteps.FromClause:
oecau join
cusms on cacsno = cmcsno
JobDefinitionSteps.WhereClause:
cacono = 1 and
carscd <> '' and
cmsusp = '' and
cacscc * 1000000 + cacsdt < (year(current_date) * 10000 + month(current_date) * 100 + day(current_date)) and
(year(current_date) * 10000 + month(current_date) * 100 + day(current_date)) < cacecc * 1000000 + cacedt

JobDefinitionSteps.Name: BillTo Customers
JobDefinitionSteps.SelectClause:
cmcsno as CustomerNumber,
'' as CustomerSequence,
cmcsnm as CompanyName,
cmpcnt as Attention,
cmcad1 as Address1,
cmcad2 as Address2,
cmcad3 as Address3,
cmcity as City,
cmstat as State,
CASE cmctid
  WHEN 'USA' THEN 'US'
  WHEN 'CAN' THEN 'CA'
  WHEN 'GER' THEN 'DE'
  WHEN '' THEN 'US'
  ELSE cmctid
END as Country,
cmzip4 as PostalCode,
cmcscl as CustomerType,
cmtrno as Territory,
cmpupn as Phone,
cmfxpn as Fax,
cmpacd as Terms,
cmdfwh as Warehouse,
cmrp#1 as PrimarySalesRep,
cmcacd as ShipCode,
cmcrid as PricingCustomer,
cmcrlm as CreditLimit,
CASE WHEN cmsusp <> '' THEN 0 ELSE 1 END as ActiveFlag,
CASE WHEN cmshto = 'Y' then 0 ELSE 1 END as IsShipTo,
cmporq as PORequired

JobDefinitionSteps.Name: Ship Tos
JobDefinitionSteps.SelectClause:
sacsno as CustomerNumber,
sashp# as CustomertSequence,
sashnm as CompanyName,
sascnt as Attention,
sasad1 as Address1,
sasad2 as Address2,
sasad3 as Address3,
sascty as City,
sashst as State,
saszip as PostalCode,
CASE sactid
  WHEN 'USA' THEN 'US'
  WHEN 'CAN' THEN 'CA'
  WHEN 'GER' THEN 'DE'
  WHEN '' THEN 'US'
  ELSE sactid
END as Country,
sashtr as Territory,
sasphn as Phone,
safaxn as Fax,
sadfwh as Warehouse,
sarp#1 as PrimarySalesRep,
sacacd as ShipCode,
CASE WHEN sasusp <> '' or cmsusp <> '' THEN 0 ELSE 1 END as ActiveFlag
JobDefinitionSteps.FromClause: addr join cusms on cmcsno = sacsno

JobDefinitionSteps.Name: Order Line - Open
JobDefinitionSteps.SelectClause:
concat(odorno,concat('-',concat(CASE when odorgn < 10 then '0' else '' END,odorgn))) as OrderNumber,
odorsq as LineNumber,
0 as ReleaseNumber,
concat(oditd1,concat(' ',oditd2)) as Description,
odcsno as CustomerNumber,
odshp# as CustomerSequence,
'Product' as LineType,
trim(oditno) as ItemNumber,
CASE WHEN odcoum <> '' and odcqto <> 0 THEN odcoum ELSE odunms END as UOM,
CASE WHEN odcoum <> '' and odcqto <> 0 THEN odcqto ELSE odqtor END as QtyOrdered,
CASE WHEN odcoum <> '' and odcqto <> 0 THEN odqtsh / odqtor * odcqto ELSE odqtsh END as QtyShipped,
odwhid as Warehouse,
odlnvl as LineValue,
odlnam as TotalLineAmount,
CASE 
   WHEN ohorst in (1,2,9) THEN odlnvl / 
      CASE WHEN odcoum <> '' and odcqto <> 0 THEN odcqto ELSE odqtor END
   WHEN ohorst in (3,4) and odqtsh <> 0
     THEN odlnvl / (CASE WHEN ordet.odcoum <> '' and ordet.odcqto > 0 THEN float(odqtsh / odqtor * odcqto) ELSE odqtsh END)
END as UnitPrice
JobDefinitionSteps.FromClause: ordet join orhed on ohorno = odorno and ohorgn = odorgn
JobDefinitionSteps.WhereClause:
odcono = 1 and
odlitp = 'I' and
ohortp in ('O','R','I','B')

JobDefinitionSteps.Name: Order Header - Open
JobDefinitionSteps.SelectClause:
concat(ohorno,concat('-',concat(CASE when ohorgn < 10 then '0' else '' end,ohorgn))) as OrderNumber,
ohorst as Status,
trim(char(ohetcc)) || case when ohetdt/10000 < 10 then '0' else '' end || trim(char(decimal(ohetdt/10000))) || '-' || substring(char(ohetdt),length(trim(char(ohetdt)))-3,2) || '-' || right(trim(char(ohetdt)),2)
as OrderDate,
ohortp as OrderType,
ohcsno as CustomerNumber,
trim(ohshp#) as CustomerSequence,
trim(ohcspo) as PONumber,
ohtmcd as TermsCode,
trim(ohcsnm) as BTCompanyName,
trim(ohcad1) as BTAddress1,
trim(ohcad2) as BTAddress2,
trim(ohcad3) as BTAddress3,
trim(ohblcy) as BTCity,
trim(ohblst) as BTState,
trim(ohblzp) as BTPostalCode,
ohctid as BTCountry,
trim(ohshnm) as STCompanyName,
trim(ohsad1) as STAddress1,
trim(ohsad2) as STAddress2,
trim(ohsad3) as STAddress3,
trim(ohscty) as STCity,
trim(ohshst) as STState,
trim(ohszip) as STPostalCode,
ohshci as STCountry,
CASE 
  WHEN ohorst = 3 or ohorst = 4 then ohisam
  ELSE ohorvl - ohscam - ohtxam
END as ProductTotal,
ohscam as OtherCharges,
ohtxam as SalesTax,
CASE 
  WHEN ohorst = 3 or ohorst = 4 then ohinam
  ELSE ohorvl
END  as OrderTotal

JobDefinitionSteps.Name: Invoice History
JobDefinitionSteps.SelectClause:
rhinno as InvoiceNumber,
left(char(concat(rhivcc,rhivdt)),4) || '-' || substring(char(rhivdt),length(trim(char(rhivdt)))-3,2) || '-' || right(trim(char(rhivdt)),2) as InvoiceDate,
left(char(oadedt),4) || '-' || substring(char(oadedt),length(trim(char(oadedt)))-3,2) || '-' || right(trim(char(oadedt)),2) as DueDate,
rhintp as InvoiceType,
rhcsno as CustomerNumber,
oashp# as CustomerSequence,
rhtmcd as Terms,
rhinbl as InvoiceBalance,
CASE when rhinbl = 0 then 0 else 1 end as OpenFlag,
trim(oacspo) as PONumber,
trim(bt.oyname) as BTCompanyName,
trim(bt.oyadd1) as BTAddress1,
trim(bt.oyadd2) as BTAddress2,
trim(bt.oyadd3) as BTAddress3,
trim(bt.oycity) as BTCity,
trim(bt.oystat) as BTState,
trim(bt.oyzip4) as BTPostalCode,
bt.oyctid as BTCountry,
trim(st.oyname) as STCompanyName,
trim(st.oyadd1) as STAddress1,
trim(st.oyadd2) as STAddress2,
trim(st.oyadd3) as STAddress3,
trim(st.oycity) as STCity,
trim(st.oystat) as STState,
trim(st.oyzip4) as STPostalCode,
st.oyctid as STCountry,
oaisam as ProductTotal,
oascam as OtherCharges,
oatxam as SalesTax,
oainam as OrderTotal
JobDefinitionSteps.FromClause:
ardhd left join 
hshed on oahssq = rhhsid left  join
hsnam bt on bt.oyhssq = oahssq and bt.oynmtp = 'B' join
hsnam st on st.oyhssq = oahssq and st.oynmtp = 'S'
JobDefinitionSteps.WhereClause:
rhcono = 1 and
(rhivcc * 1000000 + rhivdt) > year(current_Date -30 day) * 10000 + month(current_date -30 day) * 100 + day(current_date -30 day)

Name: Aplus05: Product UOM
Description: A+ Product Alternate Unit of Measure

JobDefinitionSteps.Name: Alternate UOM
JobDefinitionSteps.SelectClause:
auitno as ERPNumber,
auunms as UOM,
auaumd as Description,
CASE WHEN itbal.ibdoum = auunms then 1 else 0 END as IsDefault,
CASE auaufc
  WHEN 'A' then 'Round Up'
  WHEN 'R' then 'Round'
  WHEN 'Y' then 'No Rounding'
END as RoundingRule,
CASE 
  WHEN aucum2 = 1 then 1/auaumf
  ELSE auaumf
END as QtyPerBaseUOM
JobDefinitionSteps.FromClause:
imaum 
left join itbal on itbal.ibitno = imaum.auitno and itbal.ibdoum = imaum.auunms and itbal.ibwhid = '01'
join itmst on itmst.imitno = imaum.auitno
JobDefinitionSteps.WhereClause: (itmst.imcono = 0 or itmst.imcono = 1) and itmst.imsusp <> 'S' and itmst.impwbu <> 'Y'

JobDefinitionSteps.Name: Product Masterfile
JobDefinitionSteps.SelectClause:
trim(imitno) as ERPNumber,
concat(trim(imitd1),concat(' ',trim(imitd2))) as ERPDescription,
concat(trim(imitd1),concat(' ',concat(trim(imitd2),concat(' ',trim(imitno))))) as URLSegment,
imdsco as IsDiscontinued,
CASE WHEN substring(orctl.ccctlk,31,1) = 'A' then 'Hide' ELSE 'Show' END as DefaultVisibility,
trim(immfno) as MfgPart,
trim(imunm1) as UOM,
CASE
  WHEN imaum.auaufc = 'A' then '"Round Up'
  WHEN imaum.auaufc =  'Y' then 'No Rounding'
  WHEN itmst.imstus <> 0 then 'Multiple Only'
  ELSE 'Round'
END as RoundingRule,
imstus as MultipleQty,
imuwt1 as ShippingWeight,
trim(imcmod) as UNSPSC,
(SELECT trim(mrrpit)from imxrf where mrorit = imitno and mrrpcd = 'R' fetch first 1 rows only) as  ReplacementItem,
trim(imvnno) as VendorNumber,
trim(imitxc) as taxcode1,
immsdt as HasMSDS
JobDefinitionSteps.FromClause:
itmst 
LEFT JOIN orctl on orctl.cccono = 0 and orctl.ccapid = 'OE' and orctl.ccctlk = concat('*',itmst.imrscd)
LEFT JOIN imaum on imaum.auitno = itmst.imitno  and imaum.auunms = itmst.imunm1
JobDefinitionSteps.WhereClause: (itmst.imcono = 0 or itmst.imcono = 1) and itmst.imsusp <> 'S' and itmst.impwbu <> 'Y'

JobDefinitionSteps.Name: Order Line - History
JobDefinitionSteps.SelectClause:
concat(oborno,concat('-',concat(CASE when oborgn < 10 then '0' else '' END,oborgn))) as OrderNumber,
ifnull(oborsq,0) as LineNumber,
0 as ReleaseNumber,
ifnull(trim(concat(obitd1,concat(' ',obitd2))),'') as Description,
ifnull(oborno,'') as CustomerNumber,
ifnull(obshp#,'') as CustomerSequence,
'Product' as LineType,
ifnull(trim(obitno),'') as ItemNumber,
ifnull(CASE WHEN obcoum <> '' and obcqto <> 0 THEN obcoum ELSE obunms END,'') as UOM,
ifnull(CASE WHEN obcoum <> '' and obcqto <> 0 THEN obcqto ELSE obqtor END,0) as QtyOrdered,
ifnull(CASE WHEN obcoum <> '' and obcqto <> 0 THEN float(obqtsh / obqtor * obcqto) ELSE obqtsh END,0) as QtyShipped,
obwhid as Warehouse,
ifnull(oblnvl,0) as LineValue,
ifnull(oblnam,0) as TotalLineAmount,
ifnull(
CASE 
  WHEN obqtsh <> 0
     THEN round(oblnam / (CASE WHEN obcoum <> '' and obcqto <> 0 THEN float(obqtsh / obqtor * obcqto) ELSE obqtsh END),4)
  ELSE
    round(oblnvl / (CASE WHEN obcoum <> '' and obcqto <> 0 THEN obcqto ELSE obqtor END),4)
  END,0) as UnitPrice
JobDefinitionSteps.FromClause: hshed join hsdet on oahssq = obhssq
JobDefinitionSteps.WhereClause:
obcono = 1 and
oblitp = 'I'and
oaortp in ('O','R','I','B') and
(oadncc * 1000000 + oadndt) > year(current_Date -30 day) * 10000 + month(current_date -30 day) * 100 + day(current_date -30 day) and
(oadncc * 1000000 + oadndt) < year(current_Date +1 day) * 10000 + month(current_date +1 day) * 100 + day(current_date +1 day)

JobDefinitionSteps.Name: Order Header - History
JobDefinitionSteps.SelectClause:
concat(oaorno,concat('-',concat(CASE when oaorgn < 10 then '0' else '' end,oaorgn))) as OrderNumber,
'I' as Status,
oadncc * 1000000 + oadndt as DayEndDate,
left(char(oaentd),4) || '-' || substring(char(oaentd),length(trim(char(oaentd)))-3,2) || '-' || right(trim(char(oaentd)),2) as OrderDate,
trim(oaortp) as OrderType,
trim(oacsno) as CustomerNumber,
trim(oashp#) as CustomerSequence,
trim(oacspo) as PONumber,
oatmcd as TermsCode,
trim(bt.oyname) as BTCompanyName,
trim(bt.oyadd1) as BTAddress1,
trim(bt.oyadd2) as BTAddress2,
trim(bt.oyadd3) as BTAddress3,
trim(bt.oycity) as BTCity,
trim(bt.oystat) as BTState,
trim(bt.oyzip4) as BTPostalCode,
bt.oyctid as BTCountry,
trim(st.oyname) as STCompanyName,
trim(st.oyadd1) as STAddress1,
trim(st.oyadd2) as STAddress2,
trim(st.oyadd3) as STAddress3,
trim(st.oycity) as STCity,
trim(st.oystat) as STState,
trim(st.oyzip4) as STPostalCode,
st.oyctid as STCountry,
oaisam as ProductTotal,
oascam as OtherCharges,
oatxam as SalesTax,
oainam as OrderTotal
JobDefinitionSteps.FromClause:
hshed join
hsnam bt on bt.oyhssq = oahssq and bt.oynmtp = 'B' join
hsnam st on st.oyhssq = oahssq and st.oynmtp = 'S'
JobDefinitionSteps.WhereClause:
oacono = 1 and
oaortp in ('O','R','I','B') and
(oadncc * 1000000 + oadndt) > year(current_Date -30 day) * 10000 + month(current_date -30 day) * 100 + day(current_date -30 day) and
(oadncc * 1000000 + oadndt) < year(current_Date +1 day) * 10000 + month(current_date +1 day) * 100 + day(current_date +1 day)
